{
  "stem": "2004.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he was caught stealing potato in the kitchen, stuffing his pockets, and bringing them into the camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Now, these potatoes in no way were taken from other prisoners.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "These potatoes-- they were working in the German kitchen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They were really potatoes-- which there was no shortage of potatoes at the time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But when he was caught at the gate coming in, as soon as he was caught, the Germans-- oh, we caught an inmate with potatoes.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Poldi came running over to the German SS.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He says, Herr Sturmbannfuhrer-- or whatever his name was for-- please, do not dirty your hands on this dog.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "You let me handle this dog.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he took him aside.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And in full sight of everybody else, started lashing him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But then, he said to the German, to the SS man, Herr Sturmbannfuhrer, do you think that he has enough punishment?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the German said, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think you did justice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't think he will ever, ever steal potatoes by himself, he says.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then, he added, I would have really-- it would have been much easier for me to take a gun and shoot him.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But you did a very good job.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I don't think he will never do it again.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, it was obvious that this Poldi saved many lives this way.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "However, some people didn't understand it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They thought that he was really a tyrant.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, there was another man there, and his name-- by the name-- also a Jewish man.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was working under Poldi.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And his name was Munschni.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "His reputation was also very bad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But again, I found him to be-- he was a little rough.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But he was really also trying to-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] he was trying for the SS not to get involved.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
